Key Match Events: Mohammad Rizwan and Babar Azam formed a second-wicket partnership of 139
Babar Azam smashed five sixes and six fours in his 42-ball 75
Shaheen Shah Afridi produced a superb spell of three for 14 from four overs
Miscellaneous Highlights: Pakistan dominated Ireland to claim a six-wicket win in their T20 series decider in Dublin
Ireland's total of 178 for seven was built around a second-wicket partnership of 85 from 49 balls between Andy Balbirnie and Lorcan Tucker
Pakistan responded from losing the opening match of the series to take it 2-1
